FBIS4-15683 "drsov069_u_94011" FBIS-SOV-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 Latvia Battalion Leaves for Month-Long Field Exercises Battalion Leaves for Month-Long Field Exercises WS1104083694 Tallinn BNS in English 1919 GMT 8 Apr 94 WS1104083694 Tallinn BNS English BFN [Text] Riga, Apr 08, BNS -- The Latvian Defense Forces Staff Battalion left this week for a month-long field exercise in the Adazi district near Riga, battalion Cmdr. Janis Skrodelis told reporters. The field exercise takes place in compliance with the battalion's training plan and includes tactical drill, topography, shooting, physical and psychological courses.
